   "kind": 2,
   "value": "t3vac=L4[u]L3[u-h]L2[u-2h]+L4[u]L3[u-h]L1[u-2h]+L4[u]L2[u-h]L1[u-2h]+L3[u]L2[u-h]L1[u-2h];\n%/trivfactor[S,P]//Simplify;\n%-(4u^2-4u(θ1+θ2)+4 θ1 θ2)//Simplify//Expand",
