3.3,-528,-210,-949.7,\n-470,-1265c-4.7,-6,-9.7,-11.7,-15,-17c-0.7,-0.7,-6.7,-1,-18,-1z\"/></svg></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:2.75em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:3.35em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
