  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(* ============================================================================================\n   EXPLICIT CLOSED-FORM CASIMIR FORMULAS, two-site total (state lam1=[S,S,0,0], lam2=[P,P,0,0]).\n   These are the C2[S,P], C3[S,P], C4[S,P] the tau1/tau2/tau3 eigenvalue formulas above are built\n   from (Csite[lam1]+Csite[lam2] etc.). Defined here in ONE self-contained cell, no other cell\n   needs to be evaluated first to read these off.\n   ============================================================================================ *)\n\n(*  C2[S,P]  =  2 S (S+2)  +  2 P (P+2)   =   2S^2 + 2P^2 + 4S + 4P            *)\n(*  C3[S,P]  =  2 S (S+2)^2  +  2 P (P+2)^2                                    *)\n(*  C4[S,P]  =  2 S (S+2)^3  +  2 P (P+2)^3                                    *)\n\nC2[S_, P_] := 2 S (S + 2) + 2 P (P + 2);\nC3[S_, P_] := 2 S (S + 2)^2 + 2 P (P + 2)^2;\nC4[S_, P_] := 2 S (S + 2)^3 + 2 P (P + 2)^3;\n\nTableForm[\n {{\"C2[S,P]\", C2[S, P] // Expand}, {\"C3[S,P]\", C3[S, P] // Expand}, {\"C4[S,P]\", C4[S, P] // Expand}},\n TableHeadings -> {None, {\"\", \"expanded\"}}]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"430192\" data-output-id=\"42\" data-out-n=\"92\" data-sub-idx=\"7\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"66\" data-sub-start=\"15\" data-sub-end=\"17\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[92]//TableForm=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrsyhlke-5jouf0d\" data-page-width-em=\"39\" data-latex-b64=\"XGJlZ2lue3BtYXRyaXh9XHRleHR7QzJbUyxQXX0gJiAyXCxQXjIrNFwsUCsyXCxTXjIrNFwsU1xcXHRleHR7QzNbUyxQXX0gJiAyXCxQXjMrOFwsUF4yKzhcLFArMlwsU14zKzhcLFNeMis4XCxTXFxcdGV4dHtDNFtTLFBdfSAmIDJcLFBeNCsxMlwsUF4zKzI0XCxQXjIrMTZcLFArMlwsU140KzEyXCxTXjMrMjRcLFNeMisxNlwsU1xlbmR7cG1hdHJpeH0=\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:3.6em;vertical-align:-1.55em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen\"><span class=\"delimsizing mult\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:2.05em;\"><span style=\"top:-4.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:5.6em;\"></span><span style=\"width:0.875em;height:3.600em;\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"0.875em\" height=\"3.600em\" viewBox=\"0 0 875 3600\"><path d=\"M863,9c0,-2,-2,-5,-6,-9c0,0,-17,0,-17,0c-12.7,0,-19.3,0.3,-20,1\nc-5.3,5.3,-10.3,11,-15,17c-242.7,294.7,-395.3,682,-458,1162c-21.3,163.3,-33.3,349,\n-36,557 l0,84c0.2,6,0,26,0,60c2,159.3,10,310.7,24,454c53.3,528,210,\n949.7,470,1265c4.7,6,9.7,11.7,15,17c0.7,0.7,7,1,19,1c0,0,18,0,18,0c4,-4,6,-7,6,-9\nc0,-2.7,-3.3,-8.7,-10,-18c-135.3,-192.7,-235.5,-414.3,-300.5,-665c-65,-250.7,-102.5,\n-544.7